---
layout: default
subject: "[{{base_id_tag}}] Welcome to Cloudillo!"
---
<p style="font-size: 18px; color: #1f2937; margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-weight: 500;">Hello {{identity_tag}},</p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
	Your account on <strong style="color: #008cb6;">{{instance_name}}</strong> has been successfully created!
	We're excited to have you here. You can now log in and start exploring all that Cloudillo has to offer.
</p>

{{#if is_idp_registration}}
<!-- IDP Note Box -->
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 20px 0;">
	<tr>
		<td style="background-color: #e6f4f8; border-left: 4px solid #008cb6; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px;">
			<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">
				<strong>Note:</strong> You will also receive a separate activation email from your Identity Provider ({{identity_provider}}).
				Please complete both activations to fully set up your account.
			</p>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
{{/if}}

<!-- Feature Box -->
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 20px 0;">
	<tr>
		<td style="background-color: #e6f4f8; border-left: 4px solid #008cb6; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px;">
			<div style="font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 15px;">What You Can Do Now:</div>
			<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
				<tr><td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: #e98a54; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 8px;">&#10003;</span>Set up your password and complete your profile</td></tr>
				<tr><td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: #e98a54; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 8px;">&#10003;</span>Connect with users across the federated network</td></tr>
				<tr><td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: #e98a54; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 8px;">&#10003;</span>Create and share content with full privacy control</td></tr>
				<tr><td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px;"><span style="color: #e98a54; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 8px;">&#10003;</span>Collaborate with your community</td></tr>
			</table>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>

{{#if welcome_link}}
<!-- CTA Button -->
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 30px 0;">
	<tr>
		<td style="text-align: center;">
			<a href="{{welcome_link}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #008cb6; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 36px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Get Started</a>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>

<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin: 15px 0; word-break: break-all;">
	Or copy this link: <a href="{{welcome_link}}" style="color: #008cb6;">{{welcome_link}}</a>
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin: 25px 0 20px 0;">
	<strong>Getting Started:</strong><br>
	Click the link above to set up your password and start using {{instance_name}}.
</p>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
	If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your instance administrator.
</p>
